            //-         option(value="12") 12:00 -> 14:00
            //-         option(value="14") 14:00 -> 16:00
            //-         option(value="16") 16:00 -> 18:00
            p
                div(class="ani_form", id="contact")
                    input(type="text",name="contact", autocomplete="off",placeholder=curuser.contact, class="input-form" )
                    label(for="name",class="ani_label-name")
                        span(class="ani_content-name") How to contact?

            //- h3 Search for "suitable partner":
